### Word Count Exercise
Create a char counter using jquery. Use the base html file. When a user types in the textarea, the number of chars should be displayed below it. This number should update as the user is typing. In addition, display the following messages: <br/>
1. 'Tweetable' - when the chars are 140 chars or less <br/>
2. 'Textable' - when the chars are between 141 chars to 160 chars <br/>
3. 'Just send an email' - when the chars are over 160 chars <br/>

